OL,5, The Body Shop is set to shut up to half
OL,6, of its 198 stores in the UK and cut the
OL,7, size of its head office, leading to    
OL,8, hundreds of job losses.                
OL,10,FClosures will begin immediately on     
OL,11,FTuesday, the firm that is overseeing   
OL,12,Fthe restructuring of the beauty        
OL,13,Fretailer said.                         
OL,15,FThe Body Shop employs around 2,200     
OL,16,Fpeople in the UK, including 750 staff  
OL,17,Fat its head office.                    
OL,19,FThe cuts would "help re-energise" the  
OL,20,Fbrand, the administrators said.        
